JS & CSS when compiled to using Brunch.io to the priv directory do not work in the app.

They only work if they are linked in the cloud and/or directly in the page.

Below needs to be integrated in the app somehow without an external dependency:

app.html.eex

<script type="text/javascript" src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.0.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
<link href="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"
rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

<link href="https://gitcdn.github.io/bootstrap-toggle/2.2.0/css/bootstrap-toggle.min.css"
rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://gitcdn.github.io/bootstrap-toggle/2.2.0/js/bootstrap-toggle.min.js"></script>

